As Frostbite awaits Zardus's reply to her question of where their 
meeting shall take place, she looks to a scanner and notices a large 
amount of firepower being released over a part of North America. She 
then concentrates and a message is sent to Vampiza over a link all 
Infecticons share.

Frostbite:(In her mind to Vampiza)"Vampiza... go to the north western 
quadrant of the future united states. There are Maximal signatures, 
Decepticon signatures, X-Predacon signatures, and some unknowns. The 
Decepticons seem to be out numbered. Help them... they may prove to 
be valuable allys."

Above the ocean, above the Oblivion for that matter, Vampiza floats 
in the air, his head down and his arms folded across his chest. He 
then recieves the message from Frostbite and silently speeds off in 
the direction of the Chivtron base, surrounded in an aura of 
Chaochitan energy.
